data.description: Gorgeous 2 Story traditional home located in the outskirts of Panama City on an open lot with a large backyard. On the lower level you will find the family room is large with an abundance of natural light, with a brick wood burning fireplace and glass sliding doors to access the fenced in back yard. The primary bedroom and bath are also located on the lower level for easy access and convenance. Upstairs you will find 2 bedrooms with a full bath as well as a flex space at the top of the stairs that could be used as an office, play/gaming room, or study. 2- Car Garage offers ample parking or additional storage. Great area to live, raise a family, and vacation.
